OL,3,CPlayer brands Crucible 'smelly' after
OL,4,CWorld Snooker exit
OL,6,FA player has criticised Sheffield's
OL,7,FCrucible Theatre for being "smelly"
OL,8,Fafter he was knocked out of the World
OL,9,FSnooker Championship.
OL,11,FHossein Vafaei compared the venue's
OL,12,Fpractice facilities to "playing in a
OL,13,Fgarage" after his 10-5 defeat by
OL,14,Fformer champion Judd Trump.
OL,16,FThe 29-year-old questioned the
OL,17,Ftreatment of players over the 17-day
OL,18,Fevent.
