OL,3,CPlayer brands Crucible 'smelly' after
OL,4,CWorld Snooker exit
OL,6,F"Everything's so bad ` if you ask me
OL,7,Fif I want to come back here, I would
OL,8,Ftell you no way," Vafaei said.
OL,10,F"Forget the history, you want to go
OL,11,Fsomewhere really nice as a player. You
OL,12,Fwalk round the Crucible and it smells
OL,13,Freally bad. You go to other countries,
OL,14,Fand everything is shiny. But here it's
OL,15,Fcompletely different.
OL,17,F"The practice room ` do you see
OL,18,Fanything special? I feel like I'm
OL,19,Fpractising in a garage."
