OL,3,CPlayer brands Crucible 'smelly' after
OL,4,CWorld Snooker exit
OL,6,FSpeculation over the future of the
OL,7,FCrucible, which has staged the
OL,8,Ftournament since 1977, has been
OL,9,Fheightened since world number one
OL,10,FRonnie O'Sullivan suggested it should
OL,11,Fbe moved to Saudi Arabia or China when
OL,12,Fthe existing deal expires in 2027.
OL,14,FVafaei, who made his debut in 2022,
OL,15,Fadded: "Look at the China venues, how
OL,16,Ffantastic they treat the players, a
OL,17,Fred carpet and an opening ceremony.
OL,18,FThe players are treated like stars.
OL,19,FBut here no one looks after the
OL,20,Fplayers, before and after the match no
OL,21,Fone cares who you are.
