OL,6,F"If they don't want to lose the
OL,7,FCrucible invest some money, make it
OL,8,Fshinier, make it nicer, make it more
OL,9,Fluxury for the people. If they make it
OL,10,Fcleaner and nicer, people will enjoy
OL,11,Fit."
OL,13,FIn a statement World Snooker Tour
OL,14,Facknowledge the Crucible's
OL,15,F"limitations given the size of the
OL,16,Fbackstage areas".
OL,18,FIt added: "We work with the Crucible
OL,19,Fto make it as welcoming as possible
OL,20,Ffor players."
